headline.main: AFFAIRS AT THE NATIONAL CAPITAL.; Official Announcement of the Birth of a Spanish Princess--The Prince of Wales-- Spain and Mexico--The Nicaragua Transit, &c.

docs.lead_paragraph: Baron STOECKL, in full court dress, called officially on President BUCHANAN to-day, and announced the birth of a Spanish Princess, the daughter of the Duke DE MONTPENSIER. Appropriate addresses were made, and our bachelor President seemed duly to appreciate the interestine news.

docs.lead_paragraph: SMALL-POX HOSPITAL In consequence of the increase of small-Pox cases in Jersey City a special meeting of the Common Council was held last evening, and on the recomendation of the Board of Health $560 was appropriated for the erection of a temprory small-pox Hospital.
